⸻

eval (CRITICAL)

| eval LogonTypeDesc=case(
    LogonType==2,"Interactive",
    LogonType==3,"Network"
)

Explanation
	•	Creates new field
	•	Adds meaning to data

⸻

15. Subsearch + Join

index=windowslogs EventID=4688
| join LogonId
    [ search index=windowslogs EventID=4624
    | rename TargetLogonId as LogonId
    | fields LogonId LogonType SourceIp ]
| table Image User LogonType SourceIp

Explanation
	•	Correlates:
	•	Process creation
	•	Logon event

⸻

16. Anomaly Detection (IMPORTANT)

⸻

Country Outlier

index=vpnlogs
| eventstats count as total by user
| eventstats count as country_count by user src_country
| eval freq=country_count/total
| where freq < 0.1


⸻

Time Anomaly

| eval hour=strftime(_time,"%H")
| eventstats avg(hour) by user


⸻

17. Practical Detection Example

index=windowslogs EventID=4624 LogonType=10 AccountName!=SYSTEM
| stats count by AccountName SourceIp
| sort - count

Detects:
	•	RDP logins
	•	Suspicious IP patterns

